english.segment1: Every moonlit night. Every purple mountain. Lives to bring all glory. To Jesus
english.segment2: Every ocean swell. Every flowing fountain. Lives to bring all glory. To Jesus
english.segment3: Every star in every sky. Is loving You
english.segment4: CHORUS. Nothing on earth. Nothing on earth. Compares to You. Compares to You. My Lord
english.segment5: Every lightning flash. Every roll of thunder. Lives to bring all glory. To Jesus
english.segment6: Everyone, everywhere. Is praising You. Every star in every sky. Is loving You
